<div id="outline-container-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-1"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> What's this ? </h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">


<p>
   <a href="http://docs.codehaus.org/display/FEST/Fluent+Assertions+Module">fest-assert</a> is a great Java testing library.
</p>
<p>
  fest-assert-goodies adds extra assertions to it.
</p>
<p>
  Right now there's: 
</p>
<ul>
<li><code>DeepEqual</code> : Deep compare two objects, compared objects don't
    need to override <code>equals</code>.
</li>
<li><code>XmlEquals</code> : Compare two XML strings, formatting is ignored.
</li>
</ul>


</div>

</div>

